    Closed --> [*]

    note right of Unbound
        bind() throws IOException if already bound.
        setReceiveBufferSize() must be called before bind()
        for TCP windows larger than 64K.
        setPerformancePreferences() has no effect after bound.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        setOption() and getOption() throw IOException if closed.
        setReuseAddress() throws SocketException if closed.
        accept() not available after close.
    end note
